    "question_id" : 8157755,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I prefer this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public enum Color {\n\n   White,\n\n   Green,\n\n   Blue,\n\n   Purple,\n\n   Orange,\n\n   Red\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>then:</p>\n\n<pre><code>//cast enum to int\nint color = Color.Blue.ordinal();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
