      "comment_id" : 91709793,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Nice. It&#39;s as if the java enum is just completely disconnected from the reality of what an enum is used for... especially if people then start abusing it for things like singletons. This approach does have the disadvantage it doesn&#39;t have an easy way to get all values though."
