    "answer_id" : 41570762,
    "question_id" : 8157755,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Sometime some C# approach makes the life easier in Java world..:</p>\n\n<pre><code>class XLINK {\nstatic final short PAYLOAD = 102, ACK = 103, PAYLOAD_AND_ACK = 104;\n}\n//Now is trivial to use it like a C# enum:\nint rcv = XLINK.ACK;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3766912,
      "reputation" : 3124,
      "user_id" : 3130202,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/d068a64a7481537c0c6aaefda7eb4261?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Mike",
