    "body" : "<pre><code>public enum ProfileType {\nPRIVATE,\nPUBLIC\n}\n\nprivate ProfileType profileType = ProfileType.PRIVATE;\n</code></pre>\n<p>If you want to get int from profileType you can simply do:</p>\n<p><code>int profileTypeInt = profileType.ordinal();</code></p>\n"
